version_description:
Get 3D Touch Quick Action! Press the WifiMan icon on the Home screen, and you can quickly see the usage stats for your current network.

Plus, WifiMan now speaks Chinese. 你好!
Hello Japan. WifiMan now speaks Japanese. ようこそ!
New glanceable and beautiful iOS 10 widget. You can also press the WifiMan icon on the Home screen to view the new widget.
Designed for iOS 11 and iPhone X.
